I"]<h2 id="front-suspension">Front Suspension</h2>

<p>The front suspension has been fully rebuilt with the following components</p>

<ul>
  <li>New kingpins</li>
  <li>New needle roller bearings (instead of bronze washers)</li>
  <li>shims as appropriate</li>
  <li>New v8 suspension bushes</li>
  <li>Reconditioned Armstrong shocks from <a href="https://classicparts4cars.co.uk/">CBC Car Spares</a></li>
  <li>1” lowered springs CAHT21 from <a href="https://www.ebay.co.uk/itm/311704265979">MGB Hive</a> with <a href="/suspension/spacers/">6mm of nylon spring spacers</a></li>
  <li>New hub bearings</li>
  <li>New track rod ends</li>
  <li>3/4” front anti-roll bar</li>
</ul>

